<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Grilled Chicken Recipe</h1>
    </header>
    <section>
        <h2>Ingredients</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>2 chicken breasts</li>
            <li>2 tbsp olive oil</li>
            <li>1 tsp garlic powder</li>
            <li>1 tsp paprika</li>
            <li>Salt and pepper to taste</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Instructions</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>Preheat grill to medium heat.</li>
            <li>Season chicken breasts with olive oil, garlic powder, paprika, salt, and pepper.</li>
            <li>Grill chicken for 6-7 minutes on each side or until fully cooked (internal temperature should reach 75°C or 165°F).</li>
            <li>Let rest for 5 minutes to retain juices, then serve with your favorite sides.</li>
        </ol>
    </section>
